README

Samples written in C and using the mbed TLS C API:

01-https-client1	Simple HTTPS client
02-https-client2	Configurable HTTPS client
03-https-server1	Simple HTTPS server
04-https-server2	Configurable HTTPS server

Please note, that the samples above have to be changed to provide real secure
applications. The samples below should not have this issue.

Samples written in C++ and using the circle-mbedtls C++ API:

05-https-client3	Simple HTTPS client
06-webclient		Fetching a RPi hardware revision list from a HTTPS
			web-server and parsing it
07-mqttclient		Demonstrating the MQTT client over TLS
